
To get compile straight from source without using Cmake, cd into the Synopsis folder.

Install libgee using sudo apt-get install libgee-dev and then run the following command.

valac ../src/Synopsis.vala --pkg gtk+-3.0 --pkg granite

To compile with CMake, run the following.

sudo apt-get build-dep granite-demo
sudo apt-get install libgranite-dev
sudo apt-get install libgee-dev

cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr ../

make

sudo make install
